Anna Calder-Marshall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Calder-Marshall 0 Anna Calder-Marshall (born 11 January 1947) is an English actress. Her father was the novelist and essayist Arthur Calder-Marshall. Her husband is actor David Burke and her son is actor Tom Burke. Anna_Calder-Marshall ( born 11_January_1947 ) is an_English_actress .
